<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l34">
<add><ab facs="#facs_224_r1l1">vnd </ab></add> das <del rend="strikethrough">wöllen </del> allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> v̈mb ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> wöllen /
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dewht die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_224_r2l35">daʒ ſie <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu vns /
